litematica-printer.config.printerLagChec:
Detect packet reception lag when printer is working; 
if no new packets are received for more than Server Max TPS (default 20) game ticks, 
will automatically pause work until packet reception resumes.

litematica-printer.config.storeOrderly.d:
When inventory is full, try to put items retrieved from remote containers/quick shulker boxes back to original positions;
This function has poor performance in 1.18.2 version (may cause lag), recommended to disable.
Zhao Xianyu's code quality is not very good, this function may not work well.
